description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from hololive!
Includes navigators with voices of popular Hololive VTubers "Todoroki Hajime" and "Otonose Kanade"!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
 - Say!Fanfare! / Shirakami Fubuki
 - Sakurakaze / Sakura Miko
 - My song / Tsunomaki Watame
 - Red / Mori Calliope
 - KAMISAMA・NEKOSAMA / Nekomata Okayu
 - Virtualove / Natsuiro Matsuri
 - Right Left You You Puppy dog eyes Mecho kawaii ! / Sakamata Chloe
 - Gyu-Don Carnival! / Shirogane Noel
 - Shunkan Heartbeat / ReGLOSS
 - symmetry / ReGLOSS　*Locked

■Navigator
 - Todoroki Hajime *with voice
 - Otonose Kanade *with voice

■Avatar
 - Todoroki Hajime (2D)
 - Otonose Kanade (2D)
 - Todoroki Hajime (2D, Daybreak)
 - Otonose Kanade (2D, Daybreak)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: hololive Pack 2
